---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Graphics Projects | Portfolio" description="Three graphics projects with video, gallery, and standout reference.">
  <section class="md:mx-28 mx-6 my-0 py-6 pt-[72px] max-w-4xl">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-[hsl(var(--foreground))] mb-4">Graphics Projects</h1>
    <p class="text-[hsl(var(--foreground))] leading-relaxed mb-8">
      Three featured graphics works: a video submission, a four-image gallery, and a Cornell CS4620 standout reference.
    </p>

    <div class="space-y-10">
      <section class="border-b border-[hsl(var(--foreground))]/10 pb-8">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-medium mb-3">Project 1 - Video Submission</h2>
        <p class="text-[hsl(var(--foreground))] leading-relaxed mb-3">
          Using AniGraph to create a 2D game. Used key concepts I have learned in first half of semester in CS 4620 such as
          Perlin noise and scene graphs.
        </p>
        <video class="w-full rounded border border-[hsl(var(--foreground))]/10" controls preload="metadata">
          <source src="/videos/graphics-project-1.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
          Your browser does not support embedded videos.
        </video>
      </section>

      <section class="border-b border-[hsl(var(--foreground))]/10 pb-8">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-medium mb-3">Project 2 - Image Gallery</h2>
        <p class="text-[hsl(var(--foreground))] leading-relaxed mb-3">
          Using ray tracing in Python to use constructive solid geometry.
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
          <img src="/images/graphics/project2-1.png" alt="Graphics project 2 image 1" class="w-full rounded border border-[hsl(var(--foreground))]/10" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/images/graphics/project2-2.png" alt="Graphics project 2 image 2" class="w-full rounded border border-[hsl(var(--foreground))]/10" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/images/graphics/project2-3.png" alt="Graphics project 2 image 3" class="w-full rounded border border-[hsl(var(--foreground))]/10" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/images/graphics/project2-4.png" alt="Graphics project 2 image 4" class="w-full rounded border border-[hsl(var(--foreground))]/10" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-medium mb-3">Project 3 - Cornell CS4620 Standout</h2>
        <p class="text-[hsl(var(--foreground))] leading-relaxed">
          Featured on the CS4620 final project standouts page with Chris Um:
          <a
            class="underline underline-offset-4 hover:no-underline ml-1"
            href="https://www.cs.cornell.edu/courses/cs4620/2025fa/assignments/docs/assignments/FinalProject/standouts"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
          >
            View standout listing
          </a>
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
